### ========================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ========================================

### Registrar novo usuário
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "email": "admin@universidade.com"
}

###

### Login - Obter Token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### ========================================
### ALUNOS
### ========================================

### Listar todos os alunos
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alunos
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Buscar aluno por ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Adicionar novo aluno
POST http://localhost:5000/api/alunos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nomeCompleto": "João Silva",
  "dataNascimento": "2000-01-15",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "endereco": "Rua Teste, 123",
  "telefone": "11999999999",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "dataMatricula": "2025-01-15"
}

###

### Atualizar aluno
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "id": 1,
  "nomeCompleto": "João Silva Santos",
  "dataNascimento": "2000-01-15",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "endereco": "Rua Nova, 456",
  "telefone": "11988888888",
  "email": "joao.santos@email.com",
  "dataMatricula": "2025-01-15"
}

###

### Deletar aluno
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### ========================================
### CURSOS
### ========================================

### Listar todos os cursos
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cursos
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Buscar curso por ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cursos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Adicionar novo curso
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cursos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nome": "Ciência de Dados",
  "cargaHoraria": "2800h",
  "departamentos_idDepartamentos": 2
}

###

### Atualizar curso
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/cursos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "idCursos": 1,
  "nome": "Ciência da Computação - Atualizado",
  "cargaHoraria": "3400h",
  "departamentos_idDepartamentos": 2
}

###

### Deletar curso
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/cursos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### ========================================
### PROFESSORES
### ========================================

### Listar todos os professores
GET http://localhost:5000/api/professores
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Buscar professor por ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/professores/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Adicionar novo professor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/professores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nome": "Prof. Ricardo Santos"
}

###

### Atualizar professor
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/professores/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "idProfessores": 1,
  "nome": "Dr. João Silva - Atualizado"
}

###

### Deletar professor
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/professores/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###
